{"tid":2114111,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"提提大家，第三波武肺點黎","createTime":"2020-07-18T14:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T11:02:42.000Z","uid":245713,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0a56626875573c4f3e2dbdfcf43e5654d887fb","tid":2114111,"uid":245713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:28:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&amp;d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&amp;h=db2ec383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fr.lihkg.com%2Flink%3Fu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnews.rthk.hk%252Frthk%252Fch%252Fcomponent%252Fk2%252F1536645-20200708.htm%26d%3DgCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%253D%26h%3Ddb2ec383&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=6b6f1d3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536645-20200708.htm&amp;d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjnRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&amp;h=db2ec383</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，今年2月至5月在各出入境管制站，向獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，發出超過20萬張醫學監察通知書。<br />\n<br />\n議會陣線立法會議員毛孟靜關注，自抵港人士必須接受強制檢疫14天的規例實施以來，每月有多少來自內地、澳門及台灣的人士，獲豁免遵守有關規定。<br />\n<br />\n保安局書面答覆指出，今年2月共發出93602張醫學監察通知書、3月發出39211張、4月發出36039張，5月發出40220張。<br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，根據規例，獲豁免進行14天強制檢疫人士，在留港期間要進行14天醫學監察，須戴口罩和每天量度體溫兩次，如有不適應向衞生署呈報。有關人士在入境時，均須通過衞生署在口岸進行的體溫監測和健康申報程序。"},{"pid":"9bf50e3e2a2918a9005687260450b0bc14bb6bd1","tid":2114111,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:34:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">果班魔鬼想全香港人死</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"72fcf1a68ef77eba074bd1410ca799afd0f31ba1","tid":2114111,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"呀爺要你死你不得不死"},{"pid":"a82fcd66f3502a858a6b14ca24458030c2dd4325","tid":2114111,"uid":34154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020